{"tid":855146,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呢幾日日日都有野豬新聞","createTime":"2018-10-10T01:08:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T02:19:55.000Z","uid":89,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4fba01636436da7c1602324c9c4efdd55c23a1dd","tid":855146,"uid":89,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T01:08:15.000Z","msg":"鑽石山先後有兩名市民被野豬襲擊受傷<br />\n<br />\n鑽石山早上先後有兩名市民，被野豬襲擊受傷。早上近七時，一名女子在富山邨被一隻野豬襲擊，事主被咬傷手腳，野豬兩分鐘後再在附近的瓊東街，襲擊一名男子，事主頭部受傷，救護員到場將兩人送院，警員到場搜捕野豬，未有發現。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_341&amp;itemid=1034600\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3Fcsid%3D261_341%26itemid%3D1034600&d=pVqiA2KGJfIis%2Bm8MYXWdU4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=d5c17d8d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_341&amp;itemid=1034600</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3隻野豬北角散步唔怕洋妞 暖警截車護送返上山<br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】繼昨日銅鑼灣附近有3隻野豬在大街小巷遊走後，港島區再有3隻野豬出沒，不排除為同一批野豬。<br />\n<br />\n下午1時11分，天后銅鑼灣道114-116號外，有人報警發現3隻野豬出沒。警方接報到場3隻野豬已離開銅鑼灣道，並由英皇道向天后廟道上山方向慢行散步。<br />\n<br />\n警員沿途尾隨野豬，並截停車輛以免發生意外。有外籍女途人好奇靠近，但野豬沒有驚慌繼續散步。其間野豬嘗試在行人路旁的垃圾膠袋覓食但不果，至北角雲景道交界野豬們走上山坡返回山林。漁護署職員無需到場。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/3隻野豬北角散步唔怕洋妞-暖警截車護送返上山-070100909.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F3%E9%9A%BB%E9%87%8E%E8%B1%AC%E5%8C%97%E8%A7%92%E6%95%A3%E6%AD%A5%E5%94%94%E6%80%95%E6%B4%8B%E5%A6%9E-%E6%9A%96%E8%AD%A6%E6%88%AA%E8%BB%8A%E8%AD%B7%E9%80%81%E8%BF%94%E4%B8%8A%E5%B1%B1-070100909.html&d=pVqiA2KGJfIis%2Bm8MYXWdU4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=12faff18\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/3隻野豬北角散步唔怕洋妞-暖警截車護送返上山-070100909.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【野豬出沒】3隻野豬出城 銅鑼灣路中心Gathering<br />\n<br />\n馬鞍山西沙路輋下村昨晚發生野豬傷人事件，而遠在港島的銅鑼灣鬧市，今午亦發現野豬蹤影。讀者李先生今午3時許乘搭巴士經過銅鑼灣道時，發現所以途經車輛先後收慢，查看原因下，發現有三頭野豬竟在銅鑼灣道的路中心上，一字排開散步，間中又打圈圍攏，情景令人忍俊不禁。<br />\n<br />\n李先生稱，三隻野豬在馬路上擾攘約一分多鐘後，便離開馬路離去，現場交通亦回復正常。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181008/58770589\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181008%2F58770589&d=pVqiA2KGJfIis%2Bm8MYXWdU4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=aba72bd8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181008%2F58770589&h=6a1c1f8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181008/58770589</a>"},{"pid":"d8d09ded68e1a8c31c6567e3f83cd6e63bc05495","tid":855146,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T01:12:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eee079a52b1df375a7c13d705a25aead72a6118b","tid":855146,"uid":89,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d8d09ded68e1a8c31c6567e3f83cd6e63bc05495","tid":855146,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T01:12:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T01:14:27.000Z","msg":"加埋你三隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"612385557967e3cf5a3924a92e367a23479544e9","tid":855146,"uid":67500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T01:21:09.000Z","msg":"殺咪殺，對畜牲都講大愛，佢識撚感謝你咩，仲要有攻擊性"},{"pid":"42f830f5a6a74913153a78cca5e890a7b0ae2452","tid":855146,"uid":31927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T01:27:45.000Z","msg":"北角好多野豬"},{"pid":"78327a4f7f66864455a8861d36e390178ed0c592","tid":855146,"uid":89,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T02:03:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aae95a962414422a1928c4a01f2ddb1d8e70b4f1","tid":855146,"uid":34410,"like":0,"